node.text: Il Patio di Eataly is open for the summer - Tag a friend you want to dine with! 🌸🍽️🌼 Take a seat on @EatalyFlatiron’s outdoor patio inspired by Italian piazzas in the summertime, with their new menu of "great" items like salumi e formaggi boards as long as far as the eye can see and antipasti perfect for sharing with the table. node.text: Have you seen the new @StellaArtoisUSA Pop-Up at Pier 15? 🍺🍕 More than a place to dine, it features 6 of New York's beloved chefs & restaurants each putting their own unique spin on one of the city's most iconic dishes...Pizza! Grab your friends and take in summer from one of the prettiest spots in the city, all while sipping Stella of course 😋 See our stories for more info + reservations. (Running through Aug 19) #Ad #seaportArtois #newyork_instagram
